snippet.title: Bold and Beautiful - FULL EPISODE - 2 November, 2010
snippet.description:
Oliver confronts Amber about why she was going through his belongings. Amber uses her charm, her seduction skills, and a bottle of tequila to talk her way out of trouble. Hope tells Liam that she is suspicious of Amber’s motives with Oliver. Liam agrees to join Hope to check in on Oliver at his home. Knowing that Bridget no longer works for Jackie M., Ridge offers her a job at Forrester Creations. Hope and Liam watch through Oliver’s window and see Amber trying to get into Oliver’s computer and bombarding him with booze. Realizing that Amber is stealing her designs, Hope vows to get back at her.
